### FinTrack Pro API Tests
### Install VS Code extension: humao.rest-client
### Then click "Send Request" above each request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### ─── AUTH ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@fintrack.com",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

###

### ─── EXPENSES ───────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all expenses
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get expenses with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses?category=Food&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get expenses with search
GET {{baseUrl}}/expenses?search=pizza
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create expense
POST {{baseUrl}}/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dinner at Pizza Hut",
  "amount": 850,
  "category": "Food",
  "date": "2024-05-01",
  "notes": "With friends"
}

###

### ─── SUMMARY ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── ANALYTICS ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Get analytics data
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── AI AGENTS ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Get AI insights
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/insights
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get AI expense prediction
GET {{baseUrl}}/ai/predict
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── EXPORT ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Export PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/export/pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Export Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/export/excel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── SETTINGS ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Save settings
POST {{baseUrl}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "monthlyBudget": 50000,
  "categoryBudgets": {
    "Food": 15000,
    "Travel": 10000,
    "Shopping": 8000
  },
  "alerts": {
    "enabled": true,
    "threshold": 80
  }
}

###

### ─── HEALTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Check backend health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Check AI service health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

###
